  "interactive": {
    "description": "The resource requires user interaction before granting access \u2014 for example, the user must log in via the resource's own OIDC provider. The agent initiates the request, is redirected to an interaction URL backed by OIDC/OAuth, polls while the user authenticates, then receives an opaque token. No PS or AS is involved at any point.",
